casebody.data:
George KENWORTHY, Respondent
v.
Anthony T. SMITH, Jr., Petitioner. No. 106P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 15, 2004. Anthony T. Smith, Jr., Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 10th day of March 2004 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Beaufort County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 15th day of March 2004."
